        boolean isStackSafe
        this Line represents an instruction that does not touch A7. Note that this includes any call or branch.

      • isLabel

        boolean isLabel
        this Line includes a label. It is not possible to push before a label and pop after it since there is a branch to the label somewhere.

      • isStackAdjust

        boolean isStackAdjust
        this line is a stack ajustment. addq.l #?,a7 or lea ?(a7),a7
